section.para:
The choice of which markup system to use should be based on clear well-understood
			criteria. These might include:


Which notation has a closest fit to the document or documents. For
						example, a document with a lot of mixed markup and running text will be more
						difficult to process in some systems than others, as will a multilingual
						document;



Which notation has associated tools that perform the processing the
						project needs;



Which system the developers like the most or hate the most;



Which system will be most likely to have active support for the entire
						duration of the project;



What will be the costs and what will be the gains of each format;



What are all the other similar projects using.
